BACKGROUND.name = "Duty Bound"
BACKGROUND.description = "A solemn oath sworn long ago that only you and one other individual knows about has led you down this path. Silence is your companion and an oath not known by anyone else than you, its contents stashed deep within your mind. This oath and its contents has led you to conduct yourself in strange ways others would consider unorthodox. Your origins are a mystery to all and anything about your personal life before you joined this group. It is only you that will be able to decide when the time comes to give information and for what sort of information that is your discretion. This oath you have sworn has led you on to this ship and when the time comes you will have to fulfill this oath. An oath that has controlled your life ever since you have given it."
BACKGROUND.icon = "spawnicons/models/muschi/inquisition/muschi_inq_acolyte.png"
